    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>{{Zend_Json_Server}}, line of code 550, default parameter is NULL'd even if it exists with value other than NULL, which can cause major issues.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$orderedParams[$refParam-&gt;getName()] = null;
</code></pre>

<p>Should be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$orderedParams[$refParam-&gt;getName()] = $refParam-&gt;getDefaultValue();
</code></pre>

<p>Dejan,
Site5</p>

